text: Ryde is an electoral district of New South Wales. It was created in 1894, abolished in 1904, recreated in 1913, reabolished in 1968, recreated again in 1981, reabolished again in 1991 and recreated for a fourth time in 1999. Ryde is in northern Sydney. ==Election results== ==References== Ryde
